ge\n  * automated testing\n\n## About\n\nan interactive TreeMap visualization - Please star if you like this project\n\n### Topics\n\nvisualization javascript data canvas treemap canvas2d\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nMIT license\n\nActivity\n\n### Stars\n\n70 stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n6 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n6 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases 1\n\n0.1.1 Latest\n\nAug 19, 2021\n\n## Packages 1\n\n  * treebox\n\n## Contributors 2\n\n  * KevinWang15 Ke Wang\n  * dependabot[bot]\n\n## Languages\n\n  * JavaScript 91.0%\n  * HTML 5.7%\n  * CSS 3.3%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
